data.description: Newer corner pool home in the very desirable Prado gated community.This charming home offers an Open floor plan, Granite counters, Beautiful cabinetry, wood-looking flooring in kitchen, laundry and bathrooms.Three bedrooms and the 4th(w/closet &window) is an easy to close Den.The rear yard offers plenty of open space for those year round gatherings, a beautiful pool, retaining planter wall, stamped concrete and plenty of grass. The rear yard is prepped for your patio/Gas BBQ area.(approx $70k invested)Sellers are very determined to look at your offers. Call me(Jose)w/any questions.
